FfF pf-334_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-335_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" id="natural" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-336_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-338_">What types of Hair Extensions look the most natural?</span></h3><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-339_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-341_">&nbsp;Permanent hair extensions that are applied by a professional extensionist tend to give the most natural finish as they are smaller and can be positioned closer to the hairline.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-342_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-343_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" id="worntobed" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-344_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-346_">How should my hair be worn to bed with Hair Extensions?&nbsp;</span></h3><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-347_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-349_">With temporary hair extensions they should always be removed before sleeping and showering to avoid any damage to your own hair. If you have permanent hair extensions applied you should put your hair into a loose braid before bed to stop the hair from tangling.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-350_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-351_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" id="blackhair" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-352_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-354_">What are the best hairstyles with extensions for black hair?&nbsp;</span></h3><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-355_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-357_">The advantage of having black or dark brunette hair is the dazzling shine! Sleek and smoother styles will show this off to the maximum so going for slick high ponytails and flowing glam will make that shine pop.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-358_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-359_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" id="blondehair" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-360_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-362_">What are the best blonde hair with extensions styles?</span></h3><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-363_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-365_">As blonde hair tends to have many different tones, braids and hair up styles really extenuate this. Usually its slightly drier in texture too so it stays in place really well which works better for intricate and detailed styles.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hiCibw hHrFfF pf-366_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-hAcGzb bAQARH pf-367_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" id="keratin" class="sc-ctqQKy ioCblW pf-368_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-370_">How do you style keratin bond hair extensions?&nbsp;</span></h3><p class="sc-fmBCVi laenLa pf-371_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jtXEFf kGfXVs pf-373_">Styling Keratin bond hair extensions isn’t as scary as it sounds. As the hair is human you can use the same techniques as with your own hair however you just need to avoid using and products or heat directly on or near the bonds of the extensions. The bonds of the extensions are the parts that are attached to your hair at the root.&nbsp;<br><br>Thin hair? No problem. Short hair? No Problem. At Cliphair we hav